metadata.name: Voltieco Position #1
metadata.description: This NFT represents 1 in 200 shares of the first VoltiEco pool. This means that the owner of this NFT will be the beneficiary and owner of the underlying assets represented by this NFT which are : 3,000,000,000 VOLT tokens 1 VDSC NFT 0.5% of the revenues distributed to the first VoltiEco Pool.
